{
  "chapter": 49,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十九回 幽灵之谜\n\n本章围绕铁无双之死展开，\"幽灵\"在大厅中揭露绿衫少年是杀害铁无双的真凶，并指证其与江玉郎勾结下毒害赵全海。绿衫少年惊恐万状，被\"幽灵\"揭下竹篓后仓皇逃窜，却被江别鹤飞剑灭口。小鱼儿挺身而出欲揭穿江别鹤，却被江别鹤反咬一口，指其与\"轿夫\"串通。花无缺受江别鹤蛊惑，与小鱼儿对峙。小鱼儿情急之下提起铁心兰激怒花无缺，双方展开激战。花无缺以\"移花接玉\"击败小鱼儿，危急时刻罗九出手救走小鱼儿。小鱼儿发现救命恩人竟是罗九，罗九道出罗三一人扮两角的妙计。最终小鱼儿与罗九达成协议，联手揭破江别鹤的真面目。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁英雄若非自刎，难道还是江某下的手不成？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江某若要下手，早已下手，又何必等到此刻？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁无双若要自刎，也早已自刎了，更不会等到此刻……他方才既不肯含冤而死，此刻真相眼见已将大白，他更不会死了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁老英雄若非自刎，还有谁能令他不及还手而死？铁老英雄这样死正是死得清清白白，你难道还要他死后受污名？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里也正和方才赵庄主所说的一样，若是正面动手，自然谁也不能令铁无双不及还手而死，但若下手暗算……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我江别鹤难道还会出手暗算于他不成？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次自然不是你，你自己知道铁无双已在提防着你，纵然出手暗算，也决计无法得手的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非江某，难道还会是花公子不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早已说过，下手的必定是铁无双一个极为亲近的人，铁无双再也想不到他会出手暗算，是以才会遭他的毒手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁害死了我师父，我和他拼了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下手害死你师父的，就是你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁，我身负师门重恩，怎会弑师，你……你莫非疯了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既知身受师门重恩，便该好生报答才是，但你却丧尽天良，暗中与江某人勾结！你眼见真相已将大白，便乘着大家全都不会留意你时，一剑刺入你师父的咽喉，你以为铁无双一死，此事便死无对证，但你却忘了，还有我在这里！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你拿得出证据么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人拿不出证据，我却拿得出证据。我亲眼瞧见那日在酒中下毒要害赵全海赵总镖头的就是你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁！那日我师父相请赵总镖头前来与'三湘联镖'和解，我为何在酒中下毒加害赵总镖头？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因你受江玉郎所命，此举不但要使和解不成。还要使你师父担受污名，这正是个'一计害三贤'的毒计！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁！你……你说的话，谁也不会相信！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还想赖？我亲眼瞧见，亲耳听见你在那厨房与江玉郎商量恶计！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎会亲眼瞧见……你血口喷人，我和你拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再瞧瞧我是谁！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "告诉你，我就是那日被你和江玉郎害死的鬼魂，你们要将我杀死灭口，我死不瞑目，我做鬼也要揭破你的奸谋．做鬼也要你的命！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼……鬼……真的有鬼！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人神智已丧，若任他冲出去，只怕为害世人，在下只有将他除去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤，你杀人灭口，还要说好听的话，当真是天理难容！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你连面目都不敢示人，有谁能听信你的话！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要我说的话是真的，现不现出面目又有何妨？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位请想，这厮所说若是真的，为何不敢以真面目见人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花公子以天下为己任，难道不想知道他们的来历？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了这厮之外，当然还有那'轿夫'，在下也正想瞧瞧，他是否真的如这厮所说乃是犬子玉郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那'轿夫'怎地走了？是什么时候走的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段老爷子身体不好，紧张过度，委实再也受不了这刺激，是以方才就要他们将轿子抬回去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人太胖了，的确不能紧张，否则难免中风，我兄弟也有这毛病。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤昆仲既然瞧见，就该将那'轿夫'留下才是，此事若不弄个清楚，在下也难免要担嫌疑。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这老狐狸，若论装模作样的功夫，你当真可算天下第一。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有谁知道那'轿夫'不是和你一路，故意串通来陷害江某的？否则你又怎会如此轻易地放他一走了之。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那'轿夫'虽已溜走，但阁下却只怕已是溜不走的了。阁下定然不肯以真面目示人，莫非是做了什么见不得人的事？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友若不愿自己动手，在下说不得只好代劳了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花无缺，我本以为你是个聪明人，谁知你竟然像活土狗似的被人利用，连我都替你觉得丢人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若想激怒于我，这心机只怕是白费的了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花公子年纪虽轻，涵养功夫却已炉火纯青，要他动怒，除非……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要他动怒，除非将铁心兰抢过来是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事与她无关，阁下最好莫要提起她的名字。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁心兰可不是你的，你有什么资格不许别人提起她的名字？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花无缺，老实告诉你，铁心兰早已有了心上人。她的心早已属于他，你无论如何也夺不去的，你就算能将她娶为妻子，她的心还是在别人那里。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！好一招'移花接玉'！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你武功之高，倒也可算是当今武林的一流高手，内力之强，更出乎我意料之外，只可惜你内力越强，此刻受伤也越重。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请大家站在原地，莫要乱动！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要被那厮乘乱逃走了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去外面防他逃走，你快点灯！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这厮跑得好快，咱们快追吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此间出路如此之多，要追只怕也无从追起。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道就让他这样逃了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以他方才出手之力，被我移力击伤了他自己的手足，他本是无法逃的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这自然是那将灯光击灭的人，出手救了他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "家兄只怕已去追赶，却不知追不追得着！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令兄只怕是追不着的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那暗中出手的人，既能在我等面前将人救走，自然有出类拔萃的身手，我等既被他以暗器阻延了片刻，只怕是再也追不着他的了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，那人既能在花公子面前将人救走，家兄自然是追不着他的！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承蒙阁下出手相救，多谢多谢。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道，我并不是什么好人，你为何要救我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也不坏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却不认得你，你是谁呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听你语声，你年纪并不太大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却也不小了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自然不会是神锡道长。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若是神锡道长，就不会叫我猜了，出家人绝不会像你这样鬼鬼祟祟。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫非是轩辕三光？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不认识那赌鬼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你究竟是人是鬼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你永远猜不出我是谁的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫以为我的手脚真不能动手，你若再不说，我就点了你的穴道，绑住你，看你究竟是谁。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫忘了，我可是你的救命恩人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可不领你的情。有些人出手救人，也是没有存好心的。你从别人手中救了我，说不定是为了要利用我，也说不定是为了要把我害得更惨。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这人果然难以对付，我阅人无数，倒真未见过像你这么难对付的人……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你……怎会是你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就知道你是永远猜不着的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但我方才明明听见你在那大厅中喝话。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是我兄弟罗三，他一人装着两个人说话的声音，别人以为我留在那里还未走，自然想不到出手救你的人是我了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是妙计，这连我都上了当，那些人想不上当更不可能了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要江别鹤那老狐狸上当，可真不是件容易事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，要江别鹤上当真不容易，但你却能令江别鹤也上当。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，我再问你，我和你一不沾亲，二不带故，你为何要救我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下只是仰慕兄台的为人，不忍见兄台被逼，是以忍不住要冒险出手相救了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只怕是看见我有两下子，想利用利用我……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台如此说，未免错怪好人了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人与人之间，本来大多就是互相利用，你想利用我，又岂知我不想利用你？你若有所求，只管说就是，我绝不怪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台倒当真是快人快语，在下好生佩服。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下瞧兄台所做所为，无一不是想揭破江别鹤的假面目，而在下也的确早有此心，是以才……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是以才找上了我，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台若能与在下联手，江别鹤纵然奸猾如狐，此番只怕也要无所遁形了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你明明帮着铁无双和赵香灵，却又在暗中和江别鹤勾结，你明明和江别鹤勾勾搭搭，却又要在暗中结识我，这究竟是为了什么？好，我也不管你究竟存何居心，只要你是真心想揭破江别鹤的假面目，我就和你联盟结手，在这件事上我总支持你到底！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    }
  ],
